title: Agent Vinod
subTitle: On a mission to decipher a colleague's dying message, RAW agent Vinod travels across different countries and uncovers a dangerous conspiracy against India.

title: Buddha in a Traffic Jam
subTitle: A management student's social media success unexpectedly pulls him into a dangerous clash of idealogies, where trust breaks down and agendas collide within academic walls.

title: Kadvi Hawa
subTitle: A blind old man, worried about the survival and well-being of his son, decides to strike a deal with a debt collector to prevent his child from falling into a debt trap.

title: Jail
subTitle: A false drug accusation by a friend destroys Parag's life. He struggles through prison, clinging to hope for legal assistance to prove his innocence.

title: Sonchiriya
subTitle: After their leader's death, a group of dacoits splits up and runs away. On the way, they meet two women and help them escape their family and reach the hospital.

title: Badhaai Do
subTitle: After being pestered to get married, a closeted gay cop decides to enter a marriage of convenience with a lesbian woman to appease his family.

title: Dil Juunglee
subTitle: Love blossoms between Koroli and Sumit, two people with contrasting personalities, when the latter joins her English class.

title: Raanjhanaa
subTitle: A carefree youngster sacrifices his love after his childhood sweetheart plans to marry a man from her own community. Nevertheless, fate convinces him to pursue his lady love at any cost.

title: Gaami
subTitle: Shankar, a reclusive man, embarks on an adventure to the Himalayas to find a cure for a rare human condition. However, things get complicated when his past unfolds.

title: Omerta
subTitle: Ahmed Omar Saeed Sheikh, a British terrorist of Pakistani descent, plots the kidnapping and murder of Wall Street Journal journalist Daniel Pearl.

title: Rashtra Kavach Om
subTitle: A classified mission leaves a para commando with amnesia, unanswered questions and the duty of protecting his nation from terrorists. Along the way, he must find his father and prove his innocence.

title: Happy Bhag Jayegi
subTitle: Happy, a vibrant Indian girl, elopes on the day of her wedding so that she can marry Guddu, the man she loves. However, she mistakenly arrives at the home of a Pakistani politician where chaos ensues.

title: Vicky Donor

title: Baar Baar Dekho
subTitle: Mathematics professor Jai gets cold feet about marrying his girlfriend Diya. After the marriage is cancelled, he goes on a journey through time, seeing what it would be like if he married Diya.

title: Badla

title: Toofaan
subTitle: Aziz Ali, an orphan who works for a thug, meets Ananya, who encourages him to pursue his passion for boxing. However, one wrong decision costs him his career.

title: Yudhra
subTitle: A vengeful youth infiltrates a dangerous cartel to avenge the death of his parents. As he delves deeper, he uncovers shocking truths about his past that challenge his resolve and moral boundaries.

title: The Tashkent Files
subTitle: Following the mysterious death of India's second prime minister, Lal Bahadur Shastri, a team launches a probe into the conspiracy of it being an assassination.
